name: Nuclear Unicorn Force. Vampire vs. Nuclear Unicorns.
blurb: It's a vampire princess vs. a nuclear unicorn rebellion in a crazy bullet storm shooter for PC and XBox 360!

rewards.reward: LEVEL 1:\r\n(1) Get Kickstarter-exclusive artwork in wallpaper format for displaying on various resolutions/platforms.\r\n(2) Have your name compiled into the game (not in the credits, but your name exists in the game code). Your name will be part of every copy of the game in existence.
LEVEL 2:\r\n- Level 1 rewards, plus:\r\n(1) You can download the game for free when it is released on PC! (This is effectively a preorder for the PC version.)

LEVEL 3:
- Level 1-2 rewards, plus:
(1) You can download a free copy of a digital artbook featuring lots of art from the game -OR- the game's original soundtrack, once it is available (limit one or the other, not both).
(2) Your name will appear as a supporter in the secondary credits ("secondary credits" includes the game documentation and list of donors on the official website).

LEVEL 4:
- Level 1-3 rewards, plus:
(1) I will add a personalized signature to your artbook (digital, obviously, but it will be signed by hand using my pen tablet, not copy-pasted).
(2) You can download a free copy of the game's digital artbook AND the original soundtrack (once it's available).

LEVEL 5:\r\n- Level 1-4 rewards, plus:\r\n(1) Your name will appear in the primary credits. This includes not just the game documentation and list of donors on the website, but also on the credit roll in the game itself.
LEVEL X1:\r\n- All level 1-5 rewards, plus:\r\n(1) A poster featuring some awesome game artwork will be shipped to you. (Non-U.S. supporters, please add an extra $20 for international shipping.)

LEVEL 6:\r\n- All level 1-5 rewards, plus:\r\n(1) You get access to closed betas in which you get to test versions of the game in development and provide feedback! (For the sake of protecting my intellectual property, you must agree to a Non-Disclosure Agreement (NDA) and the beta version of the game will be set to cease functioning after a while.)
LEVEL X2:\r\n- Level 1-6 rewards, plus:\r\n(1) A t-shirt featuring the game logo & artwork will be shipped to you! (Non-U.S. supporters, please add an extra $20 for international shipping.)
LEVEL X3:\r\n- Level 1-6 rewards, plus:\r\n(1) A poster AND a t-shirt will be shipped to you! (Non-U.S. supporters, please add an extra $20 for international shipping.)

LEVEL X4:\r\n- Level 1-6 rewards, plus:\r\n(1) A physical copy of the artbook, with a personalized signature, will be shipped to you! (Non-U.S. supporters, please add an extra $20 for international shipping.)

LEVEL X5:\r\n- Level 1-6 rewards, plus:\r\n(1) A poster, a t-shirt, AND a physical copy of the artbook, with a personalized signature, will be shipped to you! (Non-U.S. supporters, please add an extra $20 for international shipping.)

LEVEL X6:
- Level 1-6 rewards, plus:
(1) A poster, a t-shirt, AND a physical copy of the artbook, with a personalized signature, will be shipped to you! (Non-U.S. supporters, please add an extra $20 for international shipping.)
(2) You get to design a BONUS STAGE which I will implement and insert into the game! [Stage ideas are subject to editing to make sure they are appropriate and feasible to implement.]
